# CODEOWNERS
# https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Default owner for everything
*                       @OWNER

# Security-sensitive files require security review
SECURITY.md             @OWNER @security-team
/.github/               @OWNER

# Documentation
/docs/                  @OWNER
*.md                    @OWNER

# Core configuration
package.json            @OWNER
composer.json           @OWNER
*.config.js             @OWNER
*.config.ts             @OWNER

# ADR requires architectural review
/docs/adr/              @OWNER @architecture-team

# Database & migrations
/migrations/            @OWNER @database-team
/database/              @OWNER @database-team

# API definitions
/api/                   @OWNER @api-team
openapi.yaml            @OWNER @api-team
swagger.json            @OWNER @api-team

# Infrastructure
/infrastructure/        @OWNER @devops-team
/terraform/             @OWNER @devops-team
